{"tid":1369952,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"成立獨立調查委員會=運動失敗？專業帶風向？","createTime":"2019-07-26T23:45:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-27T06:03:54.000Z","uid":74778,"like":6,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"c784cd170573ef832f1f9d08e309dd0ef071eea1","tid":1369952,"uid":74778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T23:45:46.000Z","msg":"獨立調查委員會成立之日，就是運動面臨崩解之時<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1369716\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1369716</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n[跪地幫忙置頂] 成立獨立調查委員會，香港人將會輸得一敗塗地。想贏返香港，請花一分鍾時間入黎睇！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1369779\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1369779</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n一個鐘兩個post，乜事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42a3292dfc8d4cd5c0777717d85c3eeed6564c7b","tid":1369952,"uid":18739,"like":11,"dislike":3,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T23:47:41.000Z","msg":"佢地係有道理，但成立左都未必會失敗"},{"pid":"998f0ec5340e149e91cee2b520958e497ce5e63c","tid":1369952,"uid":221265,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T23:47:51.000Z","msg":"半夜例牌係3毛做嘢時"},{"pid":"f22928ff8dc97acbcba6ccfb310f4e9955a2a187","tid":1369952,"uid":121060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T23:47:56.000Z","msg":"比人帶哂風向啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5a89895914327fcb36322f551a5b943a194a559","tid":1369952,"uid":12558,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T23:49:03.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">有人想拖落去唔想場運動完結</span></span>"},{"pid":"8b3ffbd7c894802fdcf24e5c55e9a8351279894a","tid":1369952,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"c5a89895914327fcb36322f551a5b943a194a559","tid":1369952,"uid":12558,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T23:49:03.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"fon